<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel gitloh a mangsa tandawk kit din!
 Pathien in A Cha changkhat neihsun ei piei;
 Tatsa gitloh a mangten hinna lama het na'ng un,
 Thilpiek a nasem dingin Lalpa'n ei sam.

[V2]
 Pieu inla, tichun piekin um un lau,
 Thilpiek in Pathien zo thei ngei puon lau;
 Pathien in mihing thil a ba ngei puoi,
 Vangsakna nak ahi ngala.

[V3]
 2. Gingchate, thupiek khauh takmai I muu hi,
 &quot;Chieh unla, Chanchin Pha thu gen un!&quot; A tii;
 A chiehdawk theilo te'n le mawhpuokna lientak I nei,
 Thilpiek a nasem dingin Lalpan ei sam.

[V4]
 3. Gingchate, khawiah go na khawlkhawm ding um?
 Thagau bawma na khawlkhawm u chun mun lau;
 Ginna a na piek ding chuh Lalpa'n A ngak zing ahi,
 &quot;Bangzat in a nei ginchak ngam ding?&quot; A tii.

[V5]
 4. Ka na za tai Lalpa nei sapna Aw hi,
 Kristien cheng Pathien thu gen dingin nei sam;
 Ka hun piei ka neih cheng leh ka sapum ka hinna tawh,
 Nanga ka hi, Na thisan in nei chaw tai.</lyrics>
<title>GIVE AND YOU WILL BE GIVEN</title>
<hymn_number>448</hymn_number>
</song>